65:0-65:51	comment	`% Adding a ^ np at end of context, insures that gap`
66:0-66:50	comment	`% is at end of phrase so no need for quantifiers. `
67:0-67:42	comment	`% Also (^ whom) is before (^ np =>> ^ snt)`
70:0-70:56	comment	`% rel_0 : prog( (^ np =>> ^ snt) =>> ^ whom >=> ^ rel).	`
71:0-71:86	comment	`% rel_1 : prog( ((^ np =>> (^ np =0 ^ vp) =>> ^ snt) =0 ^ snt) =>> ^ whom >=> ^ rel).	`
